      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i think im losing it lol. but i keep having this exact same dream every single night lately. its about this company, neurospark therapeutics? and in the dream i'm just staring at their logo or seeing their pill bottles everywhere. it feels way too real to be just a random dream. i feel like they're actually getting into my head somehow.",
